Paper: hep-th/9501110

Date: 1995-01-24

Title: Two dimensional supersymmetric harmonic oscillator carrying a

representation of the GL(2/1) graded Lie algebraAuthors: Ashok Das and Clovis Wotzasek (University of Rochester)

Comments: Latex, 17 pages, section IV has been considerably expanded, final

version to appear J.Math.Phys., Jan/96Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 37 (1996) 61-71

We study a supersymmetric 2-dimensional harmonic oscillator which carries arepresentation of the general graded Lie algebra GL(2$\vert$1), formulate it onthe superspace, and discuss its physical spectrum.